---
layout: base.njk
title: ""
description: "Xaver Friedrich — UX/UI Designer"
bodyClass: home
scripts:
  - /js/home.js
---

<div class="home-scroll-hint" aria-hidden="true">
  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256">
    <path d="M205.66,149.66l-72,72a8,8,0,0,1-11.32,0l-72-72a8,8,0,0,1,11.32-11.32L120,196.69V40a8,8,0,0,1,16,0V196.69l58.34-58.35a8,8,0,0,1,11.32,11.32Z"></path>
  </svg>
</div>

<div class="home-stage">
  <img
    src="/assets/logo-claim.svg"
    alt="Xaver Friedrich — Design &amp; Code"
    class="home-logo"
    width="472"
    height="148"
    fetchpriority="high"
  />
</div>

<div class="home-card" role="complementary" aria-label="Einleitung">

  <div class="home-card__inner container">
    <p class="home-card__text">
      Ich bin Xaver — UX/UI Designer mit Affinität für sauberen Code.
      Ich entwerfe digitale Produkte, die sich durchdacht anfühlen,
      und bringe sie selbst zum Laufen.
    </p>
    <div class="home-card__actions">
      <a href="/projekte/" class="about-link">Projekte</a>
      <a href="/about/"    class="about-link">About</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@xaverfriedrich.de" class="about-link">
        {% include "icons/mail.svg" %}
        <span>Schreib mir</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  {# Footer ausserhalb des Containers — volle Kartenbreite #}
  <div class="home-card__footer">
    <nav class="legal-nav" aria-label="Rechtliche Links">
      {% for item in legal %}
        <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.label }}</a>
      {% endfor %}
    </nav>
  </div>

</div>
